name: Ergo I
description:
I was always intrigued by Rodin's The Thinker, therefore I find figures going through either deep thought or contemplation to be fascinating. Here is one of my transhuman. Our contemplation at the character's contemplation/conclusion creates this cycle... This is one of the many things I love and feel when I look at Rodin's masterpiece. 
Dimension: 3300x4096
